#  SALES ANALYTICS DASHBOARD (Streamlit)

A fully interactive analytics dashboard built with **Python, Streamlit, Pandas, and Plotly**.  
This project analyzes sales performance across products, regions, and time, and includes  
KPI cards and visual insights for quick decision-making.

